name: Da Vinci's Last Supper by Zaam
description: The Last Supper is a late 15th-century mural painting by Italian artist Leonardo da Vinci housed by the refectory of the Convent of Santa Maria delle Grazie in Milan, Italy. It is one of the Western world's most recognizable paintings  This piece was generated through A.I manipulation and collaboration of the painting and the machine.
